# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

## [0.0.22] - 2017-07-28
### Changed
- Fixed Dom.Page

## [0.0.21] - 2017-07-27
### Changed
- Fixed HotKeys, add key `esc` as alias `escape`
- Fixed AjaxJson, change TypeError, add Error.name & Error.code, add getter & setter for onUrl & onComplete

## [0.0.20] - 2017-07-26
### Changed
- Fixed bug in Tools.MeasureScrollbar

## [0.0.19] - 2017-07-26
### Added
- Component in ElsJs.Tools, file /components/proto

## [0.0.18] - 2017-07-18
### Added
- index-test.js
- Service Toast (toast.js)
- Dom.StyleSheets function for manipulation browser css style sheets
- Components.ProgressLine
- Components.ProgressCircle
- Tools.IsBrowser and Tools.IsNode function

### Changed
- Dom.Event<Add, Remove> & Dom.ClassName element property may be Array, HTMLElement collection or string
- Dom.ClassName name property support multiply classes

### Updated
- Dom.Element.create method, add `prepend` property

### Removed
- Dom.Closest removed, use HTMLElement.closet

## [0.0.17] - 2017-07-16
### Added
- Initial beta release